To those who have come to #COP27 with the intention of promoting new fossil fuels, I say: “No. We will not let you gas Africa.”

Powerful words from our Goodwill Ambassador @vanessa_vash today.

@UNICEF stands with the young people fighting for #ClimateAction here and everywhere. https://t.co/p8RFpE4z8c

